# Platformer Game

A 2D platformer game with 5 levels, moving platforms, vanishing obstacles, and coin collection.

![Game Screenshot](./screenshot.webp)

## Play the Game

**Live Demo:** [https://liberaa.github.io/L3-Module/](#)

The game runs in your browser - no installation needed. Just click the link and start playing!

## Features

- 5 unique levels with increasing difficulty
- Multiple platform types (moving, vanishing, deadly)
- Coin collection system
- Background music
- Pause menu system
- Score tracking across levels

## How to Play

### Controls

- **A** - Move left
- **D** - Move right  
- **Space** - Jump
- **M** - Open pause menu
- **D** (on game start) - Start background music

### Objective

Collect coins to earn points. Each coin gives you 10 points. Reach 20 points to advance to the next level. Complete all 5 levels to finish the game.

### Tips

- Pink and cyan platforms disappear when you land on them
- Red and black obstacles are deadly - avoid touching them
- Moving platforms can help you reach higher areas
- Use the pause menu (M key) to take breaks

## Run Locally

If you want to run the game on your own computer:

1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Liberaa/L3-Module.git
cd L3-Module
```

2. Install dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

3. Open with a local server
   - Use VS Code Live Server extension
   - Then open `RunWithGoLive.html`

## Built With
- [learn2dgame-js](https://github.com/Liberaa/module) - Custom 2D game engine module

## Technical Details

The game is built using object-oriented JavaScript with the learn2dgame-js module, which provides collision detection, physics, and game element management.

### Project Structure

```
src/
├── app/         - Application logic and game lifecycle
├── domain/      - Level definitions and building
├── ui/          - User interface components
├── config/      - Game configuration and constants
└── index.js     - Application entry point
```

